[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1262","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1262.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1398","title":"SGI IRIX xfsdump 本地符号链接提权漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 系统中的 xfsdump 工具存在本地权限提升漏洞。该工具在处理 bck.log 日志文件时未对文件路径进行充分验证，本地攻击者可通过构造符号链接将 bck.log 指向敏感系统文件，利用符号链接攻击使 xfsdump 以 root 权限写入或覆盖关键文件，从而获得系统 root 权限。攻击者需先获得目标系统的本地访问权限方可利用，成功后可完全控制受影响系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1398"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.5.10 及以上版本，该版本已修复 xfsdump 符号链接问题。如暂无法升级，将 /var/xfsdump 目录权限设为 0755 且属主为 root，移除其他用户写权限，并确保 bck.log 不可被普通用户删除或替换。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420921&w=2","http://www.insecure.org/sploits/irix.xfsdump.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/472"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1262.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0100","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0039","title":"SGI IRIX webdist.cgi 命令执行漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 的 webdist.cgi 程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 distloc 参数中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符），即可绕过输入过滤执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.3 版本，攻击无需身份认证，仅需向目标 Web 服务发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，可导致服务器被完全控制。CVSS 评分 7.3，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0039"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.717","remediation":"建议从 SGI 安全公告 19970501-02-PX 获取并安装对应 IRIX 版本的补丁。如无法立即打补丁，应删除或禁用 CGI 目录下的 webdist.cgi 程序，并确保 webdist 服务已停止。对于仍在使用 SGI IRIX 的系统，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统，因为 IRIX 已于 2006 年 12 月停止技术支持，不再提供安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1997-12.html","http://www.osvdb.org/235","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/374","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/333","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19299","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0039","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0039.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/webdist.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-j78w-x657-xvr7/GHSA-j78w-x657-xvr7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.1175"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0100.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0100.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1436","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1436.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1267","title":"KDE 文件管理器 kfm 远程文件篡改漏洞","description":"KDE 桌面环境的文件管理器 kfm 在执行某些文件操作时会启动一个 TCP 监听服务。该服务缺乏身份认证的访问控制，未经授权的远程攻击者只要能与目标主机建立 TCP 连接，便可通过向该服务发送伪造的 copy（复制）命令，将文件写入或覆盖目标系统上的任意路径。成功利用该漏洞可使攻击者篡改系统关键配置文件、用户数据或其他任意文件，进而破坏系统完整性或为进一步入侵创造条件。攻击需目标主机运行 kfm 并开放相应 TCP 服务端口，且攻击者需能网络访问该端口。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1267"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-05-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:04.457","remediation":"将 KDE 升级到 2.0 或更高版本，该版本已移除 kfm 中对 TCP socket 的依赖并改用 AF_UNIX socket 通信。若短期内无法升级，可临时禁用 kfm 的 TCP 服务功能，或通过防火墙规则阻断 1024 以上端口的对外监听，并严格限制 KDE 进程的本地文件写入权限，防止攻击者通过 TCP 发送 copy 命令篡改 ~/.rhosts 等敏感文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420906&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1646","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1267.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1267","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1267.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1267.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g99h-x72r-vvwf/GHSA-g99h-x72r-vvwf.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87820/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1267.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000159.txt","https://github.com/RiskBasedPrioritization/RiskBasedPrioritizationAnalysis/blob/3d5cc1819ecb8cbc3aeb75d9a8260318544faf56/data_in/acme/acme_cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1436.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1338","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1338.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1116","title":"SGI IRIX Indigo Magic系统管理员子系统本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 及 6.4 版本的 Indigo Magic 系统管理子系统中的 runpriv 组件存在权限许可与访问控制漏洞。本地攻击者可通过利用该组件对特权操作的不当权限检查，以低权限用户身份执行本应需要 root 权限的操作，从而获取系统最高权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.3 和 6.4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1116"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.257","remediation":"立即应用 SGI 安全公告 19970503-01-PX 提供的补丁，或升级至 IRIX 6.5 及以上版本。如无法升级，可临时移除 runpriv 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sysadmin/runpriv），并严格限制本地用户登录权限，仅允许受信任的管理员账户访问系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1009","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/462","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2108","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1116.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1116","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1116.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1116.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-fmxx-7f4h-f834/GHSA-fmxx-7f4h-f834.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1116.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7a5a7ce5-baab-4311-a1f1-c80ac8c3aa51.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1338.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0253","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0253.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0112","title":"IBM AIX CDE dtterm 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 4.2 系统中的 CDE 桌面环境 dtterm 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。未授权本地攻击者可通过向 dtterm 程序传递特制的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖函数返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞要求攻击者拥有系统本地账号，影响 AIX 4.2 版本及可能更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0112"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.680","remediation":"建议升级至 AIX 4.3 及以上版本，或安装 IBM 提供的相应 APAR 补丁。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/dt/bin/dtterm 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/dtterm），并限制可执行该程序的用户组，仅授权可信用户访问 CDE 环境。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/878","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/333","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0112","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0112.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3xqj-xx96-hm93/GHSA-3xqj-xx96-hm93.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83084/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0112.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0253.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0102","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0102.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0040","title":"多厂商 X Window System libXt 库本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"X Window System 的 Xt 库中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用 libXt 库中 XtAppInitialize() 函数的溢出缺陷，通过精心构造的输入触发内存破坏，从而获取 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS、FreeBSD、HP-UX、AIX、IRIX、SunOS、UnixWare 等多种 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。由于利用条件仅需本地访问，在多用户环境下威胁较大，已有公开的 xterm 利用代码。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0040"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级各厂商已修复的 X11 发行版：FreeBSD 升级至 2.2.5 及以上版本或 3.x，HP-UX 安装 HP 对应安全补丁，AIX 安装 IBM APAR 对应补丁，IRIX 升级至 6.5 及以上版本并安装 SGI 安全补丁，Solaris 安装 Sun 对应补丁簇。如无法升级，移除所有 setuid root 的 X11 程序（如 /usr/bin/X11/xterm）的 suid 权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T08:41:11.703754812+00:00","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0102.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1460","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1460.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1296","title":"MIT Kerberos 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Kerberos V 中所集成的 Kerberos IV 兼容库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可通过 KRB_CONF 环境变量指定包含超长内容的 kerberos 配置文件路径，造成缓冲区溢出，成功利用此漏洞可获得系统的 root 权限。该漏洞使低权限本地用户能够完全控制受影响的系统，广泛影响部署了 Kerberos V 并启用 Kerberos IV 兼容模式的网络认证环境。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1296"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:08.190","remediation":"立即将 Kerberos V 升级至 1.0 patch level 1 或更高版本，可从 MIT 官网获取更新。OpenBSD 用户应更新至 OpenBSD-current 并重新编译 Kerberos 库。如无法升级，移除 setuid/setgid 的 Kerberos IV 兼容程序，并在系统层面禁用 KRB_CONF 环境变量传递。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420878&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1296.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1296","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1296.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1296.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-crq7-q2h2-v5r9/GHSA-crq7-q2h2-v5r9.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1296.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000155.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1460.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0103","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0103.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0038","title":"BSD xlock 缓冲区溢出本地代码执行漏洞","description":"BSD 操作系统中 xlock 屏幕锁定程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xlock 程序发送特制的超长输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存中的执行流程，实现以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多个 BSD 衍生系统，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，无需认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0038"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.473","remediation":"升级 xlock 至 xlockmore 2.5 及以上版本，或从操作系统厂商获取对应补丁（Sun 补丁 ID 10145）。在无法升级的环境中，限制不可信用户本地登录权限，移除 xlock 的 setuid root 权限位以阻止提权，或使用其他屏幕锁定工具替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0038"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0103.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0304","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0304.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0149","title":"SGI IRIX cgi-bin wrap 目录遍历漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 系统中的 cgi-bin wrap 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 URL 参数中使用 `..`（点点）序列绕过路径限制，访问并列出服务器上任意目录的内容。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，可导致敏感文件信息泄露，例如系统配置文件、用户数据等。攻击条件简单，仅需目标系统运行存在漏洞的 wrap CGI 程序即可实施。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0149"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-04-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.233","remediation":"建议升级至 SGI IRIX 6.3 及以上版本，或直接移除系统 cgi-bin 目录下的 wrap CGI 脚本。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器（如 Netscape FastTrack）配置中严格限制 cgi-bin 目录访问权限，并禁用路径穿越（..）与目录列表功能以作临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/247","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/373","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/290","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19298","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0149.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0149","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0149.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0149.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0149.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/UnAnnotated/CVE-1999-0149.xml","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/wrap.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0304.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0149","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0149.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0058","title":"PHP CGI 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"PHP 的 CGI 程序 php.cgi 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该溢出，导致内存损坏，从而获得目标服务器的 shell 访问权限。该漏洞影响早期版本的 PHP，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议用户升级至最新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0058"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.707","remediation":"立即升级至修复了 CGI 缓冲区溢出问题的 PHP 3.0.1 或更高版本；若无法升级，在 Apache 配置中通过 `<FilesMatch \"php\\.cgi\"> Deny from all </FilesMatch>` 禁用 php.cgi 的外部直接访问，并改用 mod_php 模块方式运行 PHP 脚本以消除 CGI 攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/712"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0149.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1462","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1462.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1298","title":"FreeBSD Sysinstall 信息泄漏漏洞","description":"FreeBSD Sysinstall 在配置匿名 FTP 服务时存在信息泄漏漏洞。当使用 sysinstall 工具配置匿名 FTP 时，系统会自动创建 ftp 用户且未设置密码，并将该用户的默认 shell 设置为 /bin/date，而非禁用登录的 /sbin/nologin。远程攻击者可通过 FTP 匿名登录获取系统访问权限，进而访问敏感系统资源。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 2.2.1 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1298"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:08.477","remediation":"升级至 FreeBSD 3.0 及以上版本以修复该问题。如无法升级，手动执行 pw usermod ftp -s /usr/sbin/nologin 将 ftp 用户的 shell 修改为 nologin，同时使用 passwd ftp 为该用户设置强密码，或执行 pw lock ftp 锁定该账户。如不需要匿名 FTP 服务，建议删除 ftp 用户以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7537.php","http://www.osvdb.org/6087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1298.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1298","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1298.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1298.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-jgrm-9wvf-g8j4/GHSA-jgrm-9wvf-g8j4.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87795/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1298.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000153.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b08d5461-8778-408a-8d17-7d2fc91959cf.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1462.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0105","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0105.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0042","title":"华盛顿大学 IMAP 与 POP 服务器缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"华盛顿大学实现的 IMAP 和 POP 服务器中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向运行 imapd 服务的 Linux 系统发送特制请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而造成远程代码执行或任意文件读取。该漏洞影响使用华盛顿大学实现 IMAP/POP 协议套件的 Linux 系统，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0042"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:26.303","remediation":"升级 UW IMAP 至 4.5 及以上版本，该版本修复了 imapd 及 popd 中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，建议禁用 IMAP/POP 服务，改用 SSH 隧道加密访问邮件，或在防火墙层面限制对 143/110 端口的访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0042","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/340","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0042","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0042.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/imap.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/imap_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83099/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-00xx/CVE-1999-0042.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0105.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0527","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0527.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0315","title":"Sun Solaris 2.4 /bin/fdformat 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.4 系统中的 /bin/fdformat 命令存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于该命令在处理用户输入时未对缓冲区边界进行有效检查，本地攻击者可通过向 fdformat 程序提交特制的参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖进程内存空间并执行任意代码。成功利用此漏洞可使普通用户获得 root 权限，完全控制受影响的系统。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地系统访问权限，无法远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0315"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.140","remediation":"安装 Sun 针对此漏洞发布的安全补丁（对应 Sun Security Bulletin #138），或升级到 Solaris 2.5.1 及以上版本。如无法升级，立即执行 `chmod 0755 /bin/fdformat` 移除 fdformat 的 setuid root 权限位，阻止普通用户以 root 权限执行该程序。同时限制可访问 fdformat 的用户组，仅授权管理员使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/138","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/328","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0315.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0315","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0315.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec12